cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modelling and word sense disambiguation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses neural language modelling techniques. Additionally, it could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic representations. It could also be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as word sense disambiguation is a key task in information retrieval. Finally, it could be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural language modelling techniques.
